| Plot                    = [[Anthony Stark (Earth-TRN971)|Tony Stark, the Iron Man]] hosts a new [[Stark Expo]] to showcase the new [[Iron Wing]] vehicle and the world's largest [[Arc Reactor]] atop the brand new [[Hong Kong Stark Tower|Stark Tower]] in downtown [[Hong Kong]]. Unfortunately, [[Arnim Zola (Earth-TRN971)|Arnim Zola]] and his [[Hydra robots]] attack.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.orlandosentinel.com/travel/attractions/91851229-132.html|title=A Look at The New Iron Man Experience at Hong Kong Disneyland|work=Orlando Sentinel|first=Walt Disney Co.|last=Davis|date=7 November 2016|accessdate=25 January 2023}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://disneyparks.disney.go.com/blog/2016/05/ride-tests-begin-for-iron-man-experience-at-hong-kong-disneyland/|title=Ride Tests Begin for Iron Man Experience at Hong Kong Disneyland|work=Disney Parks Blog|first=Thomas|last=Smith|date=17 May 2016|accessdate=25 January 2023}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://disneyparks.disney.go.com/blog/2016/11/opening-date-set-for-iron-man-experience-hong-kong-disneylands-marvel-themed-ride/|title=Opening Date Set for Iron Man Experience, Hong Kong Disneylandâ€™s Marvel-Themed Ride|work=Disney Parks Blog|first=Thomas|last=Smith|date=11 November 2016|accessdate=25 January 2023}}</ref>

